Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho Street
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi Mahjong Minami\NThis building,2nd floor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,8 Thousand points
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's defeated all the regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a pro, breh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just learned probability at university.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to use in Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives you perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a total of 136 tiles in Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a 3% chance of drawing the tile you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a low probability, what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'll play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ShinMiyaTei Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Yakisoba up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, here's your yakisoba. Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see what I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm eating yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're eating yakisoba NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever eaten it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the yakisoba at this place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. I get it. On the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us! I'm not exactly sure but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong and won against everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of guy is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as precise as a computer. No weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops. Thanks for the grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,5100 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've got to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'r sure winning ain't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you play me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on Ten: Tenhou-doori no Kaidanji by Fukumoto Noboyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro Takeshi as Ten Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Furukawa Yuki as Igawa Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida Eisaku as Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten: Tenho-doori no Kaidanji\N(Blessed Way of the Nice Guy Ten)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, winner just has the higher score?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident anything will be fine .Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But really I'm not doing this for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,More of a side bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, you give back what you won from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I double your winnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a ringer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to meet someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be beaten in Mahjong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore I've thought of becoming a ringer myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At the table over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A non-automatic table must be so he can cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got to be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If he didn't do that he wouldn't be sure to beat someone he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand stacking tiles is no problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,East Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest is one East South round, and whoever has more points wins, even if its merely 100 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First I have to make sure there's no cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do a single wait on an undiscarded tile, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,12,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,South Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this character? The silent type.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,South Round 2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,12,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a novice wouldn't deal into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is this guy's turn as dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm in the lead by 50,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is he playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell happened? A blackout?\NTurn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry. I hit the switch with my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenhou Chuuren PouTou\N(Nine gates completed on Dealer's first tile draw)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Ten. It's a complete reversal of 90,000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not possible. You cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is a truly fearsome thing isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on a second.\NAdmit you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you arranged your hand the tile wall in front of you moved a tiny amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow or orther it was a brilliant trick of the tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you, a pro, embarrassed to do something so childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A sneaky underworld guy like you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I could become a ringer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Don't bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Igawa Hiroyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a ringer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the business of shouldering the burden of other people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People bet more than their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether by guile or cheating outright
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to win by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy to win such a low victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you be content playing the Mahjong of a charlatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is being a Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regrettable but,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweet world you imagine is very far from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched your Mahjong very closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In that match, Ten did cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you test it once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Sawada! Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The player for this time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Player?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, he's a young one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen him play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a real estate agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Maruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Igou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, this is about a deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll play Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a deed for a plot of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm looking to get his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I already own half of his home and property by gambling and debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the remaining half,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,will be dealt with by Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada found you for your strength in Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Maruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are pure trash, but they're the most powerful gang right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to take shelter where we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means protecting garbage like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But in such an important deal can I..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there. It's clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen a lot of ringers before now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got an ability far beyond that crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Have confidence in your own Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm betting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a ringer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the business of shouldering the burden of other people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Igou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After you take his shop, how about a victory celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your mind on the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the deed like a good boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to see a contest against you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever your cheats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest is 5 East South rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is the first to take 3 rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Hiroyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the game the difference between our points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. Just what are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First Game\NEast Round One
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, Ten can't possibly cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to be vigilant against anything he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But this Nakanishi guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's collecting Man tiles, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've already got enough of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not in Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First Game\NEast Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This time he's collecting Pin tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Discarding the Dora tile after he drew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't make such dangerous discards from a worthless hand so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought. He's about to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't discard Pin tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't discard from this meld near the Dora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,7,700 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shit break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First Game\NSouth Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He discarded the Dora within one turn of Sawada's Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily no one would consider that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's certainly set a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play so sluggishly, you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's confusing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fearsome thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My dead mother left this place to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it since I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've led an honest, straightforward life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you gamble it all away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically I was tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cheated out of everything in a light game of poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I noticed they had half my shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gample you can't win against.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you become a heretic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A heretic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now you've led an honest, straightforward life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no good for this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This shop, your land..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want them to be stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,become a heretical, UNORTHODOX player for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten has been encouraging Nakanishi's single color hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been entirely a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Only,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They've put his shop on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:24:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bluff burned into his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you carry it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of catching people in tricks or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd call it more "divine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you might call it "madness."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're willing to lose it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.22,0:24:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. Round two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
